Below methods are used to Encrypt and Decrypt.

Encrypt :-
UPISecurity.getPSPEncryptValue(String msg, String enc_key);

Decrypt :-
UPISecurity.getPSPDecryptValue(String msg, String enc_key);  

Note:- 
msg -->> Request Payload
enc_key -->> Super Merchant Key

And the SALT used for the same is Super Merchant Key. Which they have got during merchant on-boarding.